  "detailed_description": "<h1>Community Hub</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119590/extras/183fd54460b7dccd4388ecb4fec35d78.poster.avif?t=1727543244\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119590/extras/183fd54460b7dccd4388ecb4fec35d78.webm?t=1727543244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119590/extras/183fd54460b7dccd4388ecb4fec35d78.mp4?t=1727543244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Social Deduction</strong>: Discover the imposters hiding amongst your co-workers. Vote them out!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119590/extras/5a4c6d26379d75736dbe33683d8cca5f.poster.avif?t=1727543244\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119590/extras/5a4c6d26379d75736dbe33683d8cca5f.webm?t=1727543244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119590/extras/5a4c6d26379d75736dbe33683d8cca5f.mp4?t=1727543244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Customization</strong>: Cosmetics are unlockable through achievements and in-game progression!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119590/extras/36aec3a00e44229bc6a843ffb076784d.poster.avif?t=1727543244\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119590/extras/36aec3a00e44229bc6a843ffb076784d.webm?t=1727543244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119590/extras/36aec3a00e44229bc6a843ffb076784d.mp4?t=1727543244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>New Daily Challenge</strong>: Compete daily with your friends on a new randomized course!<br><br><br><br><strong>Additional Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Proximity voice chat<br></li><li>Vents, traps, and cameras<br></li><li>Unique workplace-themed roles<br></li><li>Interesting tasks, weapons, and items<br></li><li>Active and growing community</li></ul>",
